        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "ADHD was just barely being diagnosed when you were a kid. Most of your teachers just assumed you were misbehaved. None of them understood that you were trying to hold all these thoughts at once, to piece together the entire plot of the Marvel Universe while tying that to the rise and fall of of European History while you were thinking about what you wanted for lunch. If was years before anyone professionaly saw you and immediately put you on Ritlin, which perhaps calmed you down, somewhat, but did nothing to stop your brain from wandering down its rabbit holes. You'd lose entire days trolling through the internet, stalking message boards for whatever caught your imagination at the moment: comic books, history, music, sports teams. Vampires was your obsessions du jour when you sire found you and realized that your scattered genius was just useful enough in terms of information gathering and synthesis. You've turned your private nerdom into a side business for Kindred, using your various and varied bits of knowledge to gain information key to their needs. There's a lucrative boon market for that. But, Seattle isn't exactly hopping at the moment, not for business, and you heard through your buddies who went down there last year that San Diego is in deep shit. There is something brewing down there, word has it that they want to plan a full scale attack on Tijuana. You have skills and even have contacts in San Diego. If successful, and if you help defend San Diego, you could set up quite the business for yourself there and establish yourself in Southern California. After all, you've not been there before."
